OL,9,     Gtraffic crash to help a baby in
OL,10,     Gperil.
OL,11,G2200F999: Critical Condition
OL,12,     GBarry was rushed into resus with
OL,13,     Gsuspected sepsis after Lucy's
OL,14,     Ghorse threw her to the ground.
OL,15,G2300FSkin A&E
